Enum XPathQuery.QueryType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<XPathQuery.QueryType>
      • org.xflatdb.xflat.query.XPathQuery.QueryType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    XPathQuery

    public static enum XPathQuery.QueryType
extends java.lang.Enum<XPathQuery.QueryType>
    The type of the query. Can be used by engines to inspect the query in order to generate an execution plan.
